message.en_US: If you're here for a fight, talk to me when you have nobody else in your party.
Well, come back if you change your mind.
Not bad. Time to take things up a step!
I'm not about to let up!
Intriguing! It's time to go all out!
Oh? Having some trouble over there now?
Do you understand our superiority now?
You cannot overcome my mighty defense!
Against the mighty defense of a Quadroguard, you prevailed.
That was fun! Stop by any time you feel like challenging me again.
Well fought, but it appears I have prevailed.
You are most welcome to return at any time for a rematch.
I was hoping for a bit more of a challenge.
Well, if you feel like a rematch at any point, I'll be here.
